<div class="postcell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
                
<p>I need to extract the text between 2 string patterns in c.</p>

<p>Example:</p>

<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c">aaaaaa&lt;BBBB&gt;TEXT TO EXTRACT&lt;/BBBB&gt;aaaaaaaaa

PATTERN1=&lt;BBBB&gt;
PATTERN2=&lt;/BBBB&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>Thanks.</p>
    </div>

<div id="answer-24696896" class="answer js-answer accepted-answer js-accepted-answer" data-answerid="24696896" data-parentid="24696113" data-score="9" data-position-on-page="1" data-highest-scored="1" data-question-has-accepted-highest-score="1" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
    <div class="post-layout">
        <div class="votecell post-layout--left">
            <div class="js-voting-container d-flex jc-center fd-column ai-stretch gs4 fc-black-200" data-post-id="24696896">

        <a class="js-post-issue flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer py6 mx-auto" href="https://stackoverflow.com/posts/24696896/timeline" data-shortcut="T" data-ks-title="timeline" data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-label="Timeline" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-7be49kpt"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="mln2 mr0 svg-icon iconHistory" width="19" height="18" viewBox="0 0 19 18"><path d="M3 9a8 8 0 1 1 3.73 6.77L8.2 14.3A6 6 0 1 0 5 9l3.01-.01-4 4-4-4h3L3 9Zm7-4h1.01L11 9.36l3.22 2.1-.6.93L10 10V5Z"></path></svg></a><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-7be49kpt" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">Show activity on this post.<div class="s-popover--arrow"></div></div>

</div>

        </div>

        

<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Here is an alive example of how to do this</p>

<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span>
<span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span>

<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span>
{
    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *s = <span class="hljs-string">"aaaaaa&lt;BBBB&gt;TEXT TO EXTRACT&lt;/BBBB&gt;aaaaaaaaa"</span>;

    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *PATTERN1 = <span class="hljs-string">"&lt;BBBB&gt;"</span>;
    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *PATTERN2 = <span class="hljs-string">"&lt;/BBBB&gt;"</span>;

    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *target = <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;
    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *start, *end;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ( start = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>( s, PATTERN1 ) )
    {
        start += <span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>( PATTERN1 );
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ( end = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>( start, PATTERN2 ) )
        {
            target = ( <span class="hljs-type">char</span> * )<span class="hljs-built_in">malloc</span>( end - start + <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );
            <span class="hljs-built_in">memcpy</span>( target, start, end - start );
            target[end - start] = <span class="hljs-string">'\0'</span>;
        }
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ( target ) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>( <span class="hljs-string">"%s\n"</span>, target );

    <span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>( target );

    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
}
</code></pre>

<p>The output is</p>

<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c">TEXT TO EXTRACT
</code></pre>
    </div>

            <div class="flex--item mr16" style="flex: 1 1 100px;">

<div id="answer-24696196" class="answer js-answer" data-answerid="24696196" data-parentid="24696113" data-score="5" data-position-on-page="2" data-highest-scored="0" data-question-has-accepted-highest-score="1" itemprop="suggestedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
    <div class="post-layout">
        <div class="votecell post-layout--left">
            <div class="js-voting-container d-flex jc-center fd-column ai-stretch gs4 fc-black-200" data-post-id="24696196">
        <button class="js-vote-up-btn flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer " data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="Up vote" data-selected-classes="fc-theme-primary" data-unselected-classes="" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-i7y5k0xp">

        <a class="js-post-issue flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer py6 mx-auto" href="https://stackoverflow.com/posts/24696196/timeline" data-shortcut="T" data-ks-title="timeline" data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-label="Timeline" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-60ql6apj"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="mln2 mr0 svg-icon iconHistory" width="19" height="18" viewBox="0 0 19 18"><path d="M3 9a8 8 0 1 1 3.73 6.77L8.2 14.3A6 6 0 1 0 5 9l3.01-.01-4 4-4-4h3L3 9Zm7-4h1.01L11 9.36l3.22 2.1-.6.93L10 10V5Z"></path></svg></a><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-60ql6apj" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">Show activity on this post.<div class="s-popover--arrow"></div></div>

</div>

        </div>

        

<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Just use <a href="http://linux.die.net/man/3/strstr" rel="nofollow"><code>strstr()</code></a>.</p>

<p>First once to find the start marker, then call it again with a pointer to the first character after the start marker, to find the end marker:</p>

<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c"><span class="hljs-type">char</span> * <span class="hljs-title function_">extract_between</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *str, <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *p1, <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *p2)</span>
{
  <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *i1 = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(str, p1);
  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i1 != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
  {
    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> pl1 = <span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(p1);
    <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *i2 = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(i1 + pl1, p2);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(p2 != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
    {
     <span class="hljs-comment">/* Found both markers, extract text. */</span>
     <span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> mlen = i2 - (i1 + pl1);
     <span class="hljs-type">char</span> *ret = <span class="hljs-built_in">malloc</span>(mlen + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);
     <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(ret != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
     {
       <span class="hljs-built_in">memcpy</span>(ret, i1 + pl1, mlen);
       ret[mlen] = <span class="hljs-string">'\0'</span>;
       <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ret;
     }
    }
  }
</code></pre>

<p>Please test the above for off-by-ones, I wrote it pretty quickly.
      return NULL;
    }</p>

<p>This will maybe not be optimal in performance, but very very simple to both implement, get right, read and understand.</p>
    </div>

<div id="answer-24696461" class="answer js-answer" data-answerid="24696461" data-parentid="24696113" data-score="-2" data-position-on-page="3" data-highest-scored="0" data-question-has-accepted-highest-score="1" itemprop="suggestedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
    <div class="post-layout">
        <div class="votecell post-layout--left">
            <div class="js-voting-container d-flex jc-center fd-column ai-stretch gs4 fc-black-200" data-post-id="24696461">
        <button class="js-vote-up-btn flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer " data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="Up vote" data-selected-classes="fc-theme-primary" data-unselected-classes="" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-g7f2ozn7">

        </button><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-g7f2ozn7" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">This answer is useful<div class="s-popover--arrow"></div></div>

        </button><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-0djpv6gx" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">This answer is not useful<div class="s-popover--arrow"></div></div>


        
<button class="js-saves-btn s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer py4" id="saves-btn-24696461" data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" data-s-popover-placement="" aria-pressed="false" data-post-id="24696461" data-post-type-id="2" data-user-privilege-for-post-click="0" aria-controls="" data-s-popover-auto-show="false" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-najvi1ie">

    <svg aria-hidden="true" class="js-saves-btn-unselected svg-icon iconBookmarkAlt" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="m9 10.6 4 2.66V3H5v10.26l4-2.66ZM3 17V3c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14l-6-4-6 4Z"></path></svg>

            <div class="js-accepted-answer-indicator flex--item fc-green-700 py6 mtn8 d-none" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" title="Loading when this answer was accepted…" tabindex="0" role="note" aria-label="Accepted">
                <div class="ta-center">
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" class="svg-icon iconCheckmarkLg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36"><path d="m6 14 8 8L30 6v8L14 30l-8-8v-8Z"></path></svg>
                </div>

        <a class="js-post-issue flex--item s-btn s-btn__unset c-pointer py6 mx-auto" href="https://stackoverflow.com/posts/24696461/timeline" data-shortcut="T" data-ks-title="timeline" data-controller="s-tooltip" data-s-tooltip-placement="right" aria-label="Timeline" aria-describedby="--stacks-s-tooltip-gtnfnrop"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="mln2 mr0 svg-icon iconHistory" width="19" height="18" viewBox="0 0 19 18"><path d="M3 9a8 8 0 1 1 3.73 6.77L8.2 14.3A6 6 0 1 0 5 9l3.01-.01-4 4-4-4h3L3 9Zm7-4h1.01L11 9.36l3.22 2.1-.6.93L10 10V5Z"></path></svg></a><div id="--stacks-s-tooltip-gtnfnrop" class="s-popover s-popover__tooltip" role="tooltip">Show activity on this post.<div class="s-popover--arrow"></div></div>

</div>

        </div>

        

<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c"><span class="hljs-type">char</span> * start = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(PATTERN1, text);
<span class="hljs-type">char</span> * end = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(PATTERN2, text);

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (end == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> || start == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

*end = <span class="hljs-string">'\0'</span>;

<span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">"%s\n"</span>, start);
</code></pre>

<p>Note: if you can't modify the original string, copy it to a buffer you can play with.</p>

<p>Alternate version:</p>

<pre class="lang-c s-code-block"><code class="hljs language-c"><span class="hljs-type">char</span> * start = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(PATTERN1, text);
<span class="hljs-type">char</span> * end = <span class="hljs-built_in">strstr</span>(PATTERN2, text);

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (end == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> || start == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

<span class="hljs-type">int</span> len = end - start;

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (len &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)
     <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

<span class="hljs-type">char</span> * parsed = (<span class="hljs-type">char</span> *)<span class="hljs-built_in">calloc</span>(len+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="hljs-type">char</span>));

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (parsed == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)
     <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;

<span class="hljs-built_in">memcpy</span>(parsed, start, len);

<span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">"%s\n"</span>, parsed);

<span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(parsed);
</code></pre>

<p>ps: I haven't tested any of the code</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt24">
        <div class="d-flex fw-wrap ai-start jc-end gs8 gsy">
            <time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2014-07-11T11:18:16"></time>
            <div class="flex--item mr16" style="flex: 1 1 100px;">

        <li class="s-sidebarwidget--item d-flex px16">
            <div class="flex--item1 fl-shrink0">

            <div class="flex--item wmn0 ow-break-word">
